TapeSection¶

class quality_assessment.data_types.TapeSection(start_position: float, end_position: float)[source]¶

Holds information of tape sections.

start_position (float): Start position of the tape section. end_position (float): End position of the tape section. length (float, read only): Length of the tape section.
